EVENT FANTASTIQUE was a dream and a team effort to introduce to everyone this past Friday! We thank everyone who came to dance and experience something magical and for your support of the Youth Music Project!

Very Special THANK YOU to:

Adrianna Hill Grand Ballroom - Jessie, Tim and their wonderful staff made it easy to work around the many weddings and events that happen in this beautiful venue but we always felt like we were their priority!

Al Jones Productions - Al Jones and Donovan Fraser made what can be an acoustical challenge into a perfect sounding show!

Brenda Adams and Victor Bingham - The light design and programming were beyond what we asked for but you kept coming up with new ideas to make our night unique!

VideoMedia - Dan Pred - Thank you for filming what was a memorable night of artistry and music!

Jennifer Yamashiro and Valerie O'Keefe - Managing check in and hospitality is a big job but you both made it effortless!

Roger Collier - Thank you for the little things that make a BIG difference in our night! You are invaluable!

DJ Bomb Shel Bailey - Your spirit and professionalism was inspiring to witness and be around! I hope we can do this more often! It was nice to have you in Portland!

Throwback - Nick Gimarelli, Jared Watson, Niko Tonido and Kaleb Rankin - You rocked like Big Dogs!!! The future of rock is safe! Ima Starman, Mindy Gimarelli and Brad Watson are an amazing group of "roadies"! Kevin Rankin, you were missed!

The Nu Wavers - Willow Bacon. Steve Adams. Steve Hale. Kenny Davis - You put on an amazing show and are the best sports when asked to do anything! Let's have some fun and adventure!!! Aerial Muse Collective - Rebecca Palmer. Treya Bushell. Brittany Ashworth - Thank you for all of your time and planning in being a part of Event Fantastique! We had logistical challenges that were solved with innovation and motivation! Thank you for your supreme efforts! Your performances were beautiful and inspiring as always!
